entries.title: Deliver Jabba's Gifts to Imperial VIP's (continued)
entries.split_quest_alert: Lastly, you must offer a small gift to an Imperial Inquisitor who's coming to visit the prison satellite...
entries.hello_p: Good to see you, pilot! I have your delivery ready for transfer.
entries.hello_d: Who are you?! Are you the delivery ship? We cannot stay here long!
entries.found_loc_p: Fly to this location and meet our transport.
entries.found_loc_d: Got an update for you... follow this waypoint. Meet up with the Seinar Systems legal counsel.
entries.docking_started_pickup: Hey there. Got blank documents here... ready for transfer to the Seinar Systems legal counsel.
entries.docking_complete_pickup: All right! All of the blank documents should be transferred.
entries.docking_complete_delivery: Excellent! This is a fabulous prize, my friend! Tell Jabba that we are open to his requests... whatever they may be.
entries.attack_notify: Enemy craft detected on attack vector.
entries.arrived_at_pickup: Your delivery target (the Seinar Systems legal counsel) should be here very soon...
entries.arrived_at_delivery: The transport should be here shortly...
